changed a lot, don't you?

156
00:12:16,670 --> 00:12:18,280
But you and I both know it hasn't.

157
00:12:19,080 --> 00:12:21,150
And you haven't changed either.

158
00:12:22,050 --> 00:12:23,350
You know what I mean, don't you?

159
